trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection?displayProperty=nameWithType> is returned from the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType> class.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection?displayProperty=nameWithType> se devuelve desde el <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>, y <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A> métodos de la <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType> clase.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> objects returned by the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A> methods contain a snapshot of user information in the membership data store.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> objetos devueltos por la <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>, y <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A> métodos contienen una instantánea de la información de usuario en el almacén de datos de pertenencia.

trans-unit.source: That is, changes to the membership user information in a <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> are not reflected in the membership data store.
trans-unit.target: Es decir, cambia a la información de usuario de pertenencia en una <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> no se reflejan en el almacén de datos de pertenencia.

trans-unit.source: To modify membership user information in the membership data store, use the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType> class.
trans-unit.target: Para modificar la información de usuario de pertenencia en el almacén de datos de pertenencia, utilice el <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A> y <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> métodos de la <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType> clase.

trans-unit.source: If you are not familiar with the membership features of ASP.NET, see [Introduction to Membership](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/79184d17-f4c7-4c9f-a073-cec4f5543980) before continuing.
trans-unit.target: Si no está familiarizado con las características de pertenencia de ASP.NET, vea [Introducción a la suscripción](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/79184d17-f4c7-4c9f-a073-cec4f5543980) antes de continuar.

trans-unit.source: For a list of other topics related to membership, see [Managing Users by Using Membership](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/824c3a24-f0af-427c-a652-0d2d1e9397cd).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener una lista de otros temas relacionados con la pertenencia, vea [administrar usuarios mediante pertenencia](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/824c3a24-f0af-427c-a652-0d2d1e9397cd).

trans-unit.source: That is, changes to the membership user information in the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> are not reflected in the membership data store.
trans-unit.target: Es decir, cambia a la información de usuario de pertenencia en el <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> no se reflejan en el almacén de datos de pertenencia.

trans-unit.source: To modify membership user information in the membership data store, use the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Para modificar la información de usuario de pertenencia en el almacén de datos de pertenencia, utilice el <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A>, y <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.target: Quita el objeto de usuario de pertenencia con el nombre de usuario especificado de la colección.

trans-unit.source: The collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: La colección es de solo lectura.

trans-unit.source: Makes the contents of the membership user collection read-only.
trans-unit.target: Hace que el contenido de la colección de usuarios de pertenencia sea de solo lectura.

trans-unit.source: The contents of a <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> are considered read-only, as they are a snapshot of the membership user information in the membership data store.
trans-unit.target: El contenido de un <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> se consideran de solo lectura, ya que son una instantánea de la información de usuario de pertenencia en el almacén de datos de pertenencia.

trans-unit.source: Membership user information is modified using the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Información de usuario de pertenencia se modifica con el <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A> y <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method marks the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> as read-only so that <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> objects cannot be added to or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> método marcas el <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> como de solo lectura para que <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> no se agregan o se quita de la colección de objetos.

trans-unit.source: Property values for the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> objects are not marked as read-only.
trans-unit.target: Valores de propiedad para el <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> objetos no están marcados como de solo lectura.

trans-unit.source: That is, you can modify the property values of a <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> in the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> regardless of whether the collection has been marked as read-only by the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Es decir, puede modificar los valores de propiedad de un <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> en el <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> independientemente de si la colección se ha marcado como de solo lectura mediante el <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> método.
